-----------------------------------------------------------------------
Working code that provides a starting point for LDAP Authentication and Group Membership checking. Uses ruby-net-ldap library to avoid native dependency.

USAGE:
* Edit rename ldap.yml and edit for your environment.
* ruby example.rb

Only tested against Active Directory.



